  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class IrisProjectApplication
extends android.app.Application
    IrisProjectApplication is the main class to start our app. This class will initialize all the global states of models which can then allow our activity controllers to populate it.
    Author:
    itstc, anticobalt
